@node "Main" "MultiPack - Multi-format message packer for DLG Proffessional"

                          @{b}@{u}@{fg shadow}MultiPack v1.4@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}
                          By:  @{"Jay Ruyle" link "Author" 0}


MultiPack is a multi-format message packer for DLG Professional. It is used by users to pack up unread mail and have it placed in an archive in their private file directory.  It can be used in conjunction with various off-line readers to allow the user t 


MultiPack currently supports three formats:

 o ASCII    -- providing much the same functionality as DLG's MailPack.
 o QWK      -- providing packing/unpacking of QWK bundles.
 o BlueWave -- providing packing/unpacking of BlueWave bundles.

Since MultiPack supports different formats through the use of shared libraries, adding new formats consists only of dropping the .library files in your LIBS: directory.

